## Visual Studio Backup generated file
*~

## Visual Studio 2015 cache/options directory
.vs/

## Nuget packages
*.nupkg
# The packages folder can be ignored because of Package Restore
**/[Pp]ackages/*
# except build/, which is used as an MSBuild target.
!**/[Pp]ackages/build/
# Uncomment if you don't want to check in your restored packages
#!**/[Pp]ackages/

